+.. _V4L2_PIX_FMT_P010:
+
+P010
+----
+
+The number of bytes in one luminance row must be divisible by 16,
+which means there will be padded 0 in the right edge when necessary.
+
+.. raw:: latex
+
+    \begingroup
+    \small
+    \setlength{\tabcolsep}{2pt}
